Xi Jinping sends congratulatory letter to the 2021 Greater Bay Area Science Forum - Xinhua News
Message from Beijing of the Xinhua News Agency on December 11: President Xi Jinping gave a congratulatory letter to the Science Forum of the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau Greater Bay Area of 2021.
As pointed by Xi Jinping, the world today is experiencing a huge change that did not happen during the last 100 years, and global scientific and technological innovation has entered into a intensive active phase, and a new round of scientific and technological revolution and industrial revolution has resulted in profound influences on global economic structure.
It is necessary for Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau Greater Bay Area to construct global scientific and technological innovation highlands around constructing an international scientific and technological innovation center, to promote the development of the emerging industry.
China is willing to work together with scientists of various countries and international scientific and technological organizations to promote international scientific and technological exchange and cooperation, strengthen research on great scientific problems, facilitate general scientific and technological difficulty solving and deepen cooperation in key scientific projects, to promote the development of global scientific understanding and bring in benefits of mankind.
The Scientific Forum of Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau Greater Bay Area of 2021 was opened in Guangzhou, Guangdong, with the theme of “exploring the future and sharing the science”, hosted by People’s Government of Guangdong Province.